{"type": "article", "id": 30696, "title": "便携灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-07T22:52:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160807192427tJ7035ZS9UV6MqY8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>你见过可以用“片”作量词的灯吗？<a href=\"http://studiobananathings.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">STUDIO BANANA THiNGS</a> 推出的 Kangaroo Light 就是这么一“片”会发光的“毯子”。它是一款仅重 149 克、12 毫米厚的便携式灯具，正六边形的硅胶灯罩可以根据需要折叠成各种形状，兼具实用性与装饰性。除了用作夜灯或者气氛灯之外，你还可以把它放在包内随身携带，这样就不用担心在一片漆黑的情况下在包里手忙脚乱地翻找物品了。这是它的<a href=\"http://studiobananathings.com/products/kangaroo-light\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格为 75.99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807200046BdFs9OvpYU0hTnJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807200046kDpi5sABFPIuyMHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807200046sIxtCyD09RUwhNa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807200047MCmsw9I60nrDK2Va.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}